knowledgeElements.name: Analytical and Critical Thinking
knowledgeElements.meaning: A mental process of simplifying complex information into basic parts and evaluating results to make proper decisions

knowledgeElements.name: Collaboration and Teamwork
knowledgeElements.meaning: Apportion challenging tasks into simpler ones and then work together to complete them efficiently

knowledgeElements.name: Ethical and Intercultural Perspectives
knowledgeElements.meaning: Ethical perspectives of the different viewpoints someone uses to view a problem in the context of individual human values

knowledgeElements.name: Mathematics and Statistics
knowledgeElements.meaning: Use of numbers and theories abstractly especially in the collection and analysis of numerical data

knowledgeElements.name: Multi-Task Prioritization and Management
knowledgeElements.meaning: Processing several issues or tasks at once while arranging them according to importance to do specific one first

knowledgeElements.name: Oral Communication and Presentation
knowledgeElements.meaning: Conveying a message orally using real-time presentations with visual aids related audience interests and goals

knowledgeElements.name: Problem Solving and Trouble Shooting
knowledgeElements.meaning: A logical and orderly search for the source of a unit problem and making the unit operational again

knowledgeElements.name: Project and Task Organization and Planning
knowledgeElements.meaning: A process to provide decisions about a project concerning organization and planning to achieve a successful result

knowledgeElements.name: Quality Assurance / Control
knowledgeElements.meaning: Use of techniques, methods, and processes to identify and prevent defects according to defined quality standards

knowledgeElements.name: Relationship Management
knowledgeElements.meaning: A strategy to maintain an ongoing level of engagement usually between a business and its customers or other businesses

dispositions.name: Adaptable
dispositions.meaning: Flexible; agile, adjust in response to change

dispositions.name: Collaborative
dispositions.meaning: Team player, willing to work with others

dispositions.name: Purpose-driven
dispositions.meaning: Goal driven, achieve goals, business acumen
